‎我知道我没得到这份工作
I know I didn't get the job,

00:10:54.500 --> 00:10:55.790
‎这没关系
and that's totally cool.

00:10:56.700 --> 00:10:59.250
‎但这是我生平最尴尬的求职面试
But that was the most awkward job interview of my entire life.

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:02.830
‎我想我们该为此干杯 温格雷夫先生
So, I think we should toast to it, Mr. Wingrave.

00:11:06.790 --> 00:11:08.410
‎还是你更喜欢喝茶
Or do you prefer it in your tea?

00:11:11.410 --> 00:11:12.410
‎那么...
So...

00:11:12.790 --> 00:11:14.500
‎现在你可以告诉我吗
you can tell me now, right?

00:11:15.410 --> 00:11:17.200
‎我真的很好奇
I'm honestly so, so curious.

00:11:17.950 --> 00:11:18.950
‎好奇什么
About what?

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:22.040
‎隐情
The catch.

